{"tid":818322,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"暫時an機得三星One Plus同小米買得過","createTime":"2018-09-14T04:32:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-14T06:13:15.000Z","uid":52215,"like":6,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"53b05030bd00fe0e2035a2b8d5fc483038a3cb35","tid":818322,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T04:32:16.000Z","msg":"三星，最流行，旗艦機硬件最強<br />\nOne plus, 大陸品牌for國際巿場，旗艦硬件又唔貴<br />\n小米，平，硬件ok, 香港有service center<br />\n<br />\n其他an品牌真係可以消失<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"597ace9923fee9011deec376e7054f068b4fd436","tid":818322,"uid":205710,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T04:33:12.000Z","msg":"習大人：而家歐洲嗰邊開始多人用華為啦，華為你地要繼續努力啊&hellip;<br />\n華為發言人：係嘅，習大人<br />\n<br />\n習大人：另外oneplus有好多連登仔用緊，個post入面仲要係正當討論而唔係圍屌，我非常滿意，記住加強產品質素。咁就會令更多連登仔用，可以方便監控。<br />\noneplus發言人：我地會加強隱藏監控程式更難被發現，咁就可以令連登仔繼續用我地部電話啦<br />\n<br />\n習大人：你地兩個都做得非常好&hellip;&hellip;哈哈哈哈<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57f2d8962e1ed7cf7cc5f32c8fad998bb9edd8f2","tid":818322,"uid":73310,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T04:52:34.000Z","msg":"大家無視呢個post，等個post沉左佢<br />\n唔好助長啲支那牌子電話打手<br />\n唔好回<br />\n亦都唔好正/負皮，唔洗任何比存在感佢<br />\n就算個內容好似讚埋samsung，但起碼佢已經做到個兩部支那機個名經常曝光係連登到<br />\n屌佢都冇意義，佢只係想引起討論<br />\n由佢同佢啲同事自己推飽佢<br />\n<br />\nps: 提醒大家後，我都唔會再覆呢個post"},{"pid":"c74b63b33f0b26fa6a4e9e7140dc42e5d7b2d2db","tid":818322,"uid":140167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T04:53:52.000Z","msg":"你個名"},{"pid":"95a31e04aa069101c0ef56f57ef670c6b278a0dc","tid":818322,"uid":74530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T04:55:09.000Z","msg":"Nokia？"},{"pid":